==Mandarin==
Literally: One cannot get fish and bear's paw at the same time.
===Proverb===
{{cmn-proverb|s|pin=yú yŭ xióng zhăng bù kĕ jiān dé|pint=yu2yu3xiong2zhang3bu4ke3jian1de2|tra=魚與熊掌不可兼得|sim=鱼与熊掌不可兼得|rs=鱼00}}
